{"tid":1480622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李慧琼：見到不少參與者手持國旗 令我深受感動","createTime":"2019-08-17T11:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:04:11.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"37c54606633a7f21f040323441915a619ea09407","tid":1480622,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"今日是第三次反暴力、撐警方既集會。雖然三次集會的天氣都不算好，有風有雨，一如香港社會目前正處於風雨飄搖，但無阻市民反暴力、救香港的決心，令我深受感動。<br />\n<br />\n另一個很感動是見到不少參與者手持國旗，部分是團體在場派發，但有更多是參與市民自發帶來，反映大家都心繫祖國，愛護香港。<br />\n<br />\n我要嚴正向暴力示威者指出，弄污國旗、毀損國徽是侮辱國家及挑戰國家主權的極端行為，是對一國兩制的嚴重挑戰，如果再不收手，等如推香港去萬劫不復的境地，是最傷害香港的行為。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LeeWaiKingStarry/posts/1975656922535365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLeeWaiKingStarry%2Fposts%2F1975656922535365&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=86c722f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LeeWaiKingStarry/posts/1975656922535365</a>"},{"pid":"acfe068a14b16b2fb3faedefc391f53f31f94dc8","tid":1480622,"uid":143230,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"完左之後d國旗咪又係全部垃圾筒見<br />\n護旗手做左野未?"},{"pid":"f821e258fdf1360033a54642cc4010ab520c4bdd","tid":1480622,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09159cb3440f81e8e02014d2f915a52098cc2a6","tid":1480622,"uid":254788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"萬劫不復？聽落好撚正咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a57d10f99285244bd9501afb0b196b322af7951","tid":1480622,"uid":34816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:37:13.000Z